Final quality checklist for all 50 projects
- Reproducible run instructions in README.
- Clear input and output contract.
- Error handling for common failures (missing file, bad input, network/API issues).
- At least one example dataset or sample file.
- Saved outputs (plots, model, or reports) for quick verification.